{"version": "0.2.0-beta.6", "title": "Shin Seiki Evangelion", "title_uuid": "cc3209cd-c119-4870-b06c-9a34f447db7e", "volume": "Shin Seiki Evangelion 9", "volume_uuid": "912fc62b-b27c-4321-9310-1e02e618e798", "pages": [{"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1453, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [86, 387, 364, 887], "vertical": false, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["貞本義行", "スピードに爽快感。操縦性に充実感。", "美しいフォル。ムに所有欲が満たされ", "る．．．。", "いやあ、本当にスポーツカーってい", "いもんですね。", "一方恋愛はいくら、愛情とお金と時", "間を費やしても車のように確実な見", "返りはないけど、これまた、底知れぬ", "魅力があります。", "たとえ対象がアイドルや二次元の隅", "像であっても、時として男はＤＮＡに", "突き動かされた、ただの哀れな雄と", "なってしまいます。", "車女性、芸術独国。酒が欠けるけど、", "それらは私の原動力かもしれません。", "おお．．．こう書くと、オレって刹那に満", "ちたラテンの人みたいざまえ。"]}, {"box": [75, 408, 357, 901], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["しかし、これからは、"]}, {"box": [71, 1152, 368, 1172], "vertical": false, "font_size": 12.0, "lines": ["ＣＤＶＥＲＴＴＥＳＥＮＶ／ＫＡＺＵＡＮＴＡＤＡＨＨＯ「ＢＥＥＮＴＯ"]}, {"box": [743, 28, 1041, 112], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["茅能也糸已"]}, {"box": [1329, 153, 1400, 330], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["新世紀"]}, {"box": [1038, 283, 1266, 375], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["．．．ｄｕｍｅ", "アイフステルドレス"]}, {"box": [1312, 259, 1417, 707], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ラァンゲリオン、"]}, {"box": [898, 1038, 945, 1062], "vertical": false, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["漫画"]}, {"box": [1062, 1090, 1286, 1148], "vertical": false, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["ＹｏｕＴｕｂｅＫｉｓｉＤＡＭＯＴＯ", "原作／ＧＡＩＮＡＸ"]}, {"box": [1323, 801, 1410, 1113], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["『自本義行", "原作ＧＡＩＮＡＸ"]}, {"box": [1328, 1147, 1403, 1187], "vertical": false, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["ＫＣＡＩ２－９", "角川書店"]}], "img_path": "000-1.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1404, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [1, 106, 87, 144], "vertical": false, "font_size": 12.0, "lines": ["Ｃｏｒｍｅｓ"]}, {"box": [13, 156, 75, 270], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["で、新世紀丁寧"]}, {"box": [168, 62, 384, 170], "vertical": false, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["９７８４０４７１３６１８２"]}, {"box": [169, 136, 381, 168], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["１０月１０日－１１月２９ア８４０４７１３６１８２"]}, {"box": [170, 202, 389, 305], "vertical": false, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["１９：１９２０９７７９００５４０２"]}, {"box": [445, 55, 737, 139], "vertical": false, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["ＩＳＢＮ４－Ｏ４－７１３６１８－２", "ｃＯ９７９＼５４０Ｅ"]}, {"box": [443, 193, 769, 223], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["定価：本体５４０円〈税別角川書店"]}, {"box": [0, 351, 93, 571], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["アンゲリエ"]}, {"box": [0, 799, 90, 1113], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["貞本義行", "原作ＧＡＩＮＡＸ"]}, {"box": [5, 1149, 82, 1187], "vertical": false, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["ＫＣＡＩ２９", "角川書店"]}], "img_path": "000-2.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1599, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [53, 214, 278, 361], "vertical": false, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["漫画「長く", "ＹｏｕＴｈｉｔｏＫｉｓｔＤＡＭのＴＯ", "原作ヲ〈ＧＡＮＩＡＸ"]}], "img_path": "001.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 1600, "img_height": 1144, "blocks": [], "img_path": "002-003.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 800, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [240, 158, 580, 248], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＰＲＯＧＲＡＭ"]}, {"box": [329, 257, 497, 280], "vertical": false, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["ＥｖＡＮＧＥＬＩＯＮ９"]}, {"box": [144, 407, 387, 522], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＳＴＡＲＥ５８－拒絶", "ＳＩＡＥＥ５９プライド"]}, {"box": [149, 564, 367, 605], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＳＩＭＥ．ＧＯ・ドール"]}, {"box": [152, 331, 530, 365], "vertical": false, "font_size": 30.0, "lines": ["ＳＩＭＥＢフィフスチルドレン"]}, {"box": [149, 808, 360, 844], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＳＩｎＥ．６３応戦"]}, {"box": [153, 649, 493, 684], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＳＩＭＥＴＩロンギヌスの槍"]}, {"box": [147, 727, 454, 766], "vertical": false, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["ＳＴＭＥ３２．ｄｉｓｔａｎｃｅ"]}, {"box": [607, 357, 691, 856], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["２９５３７７１０１１２５１４９"]}, {"box": [284, 955, 572, 972], "vertical": false, "font_size": 15.0, "lines": ["５０ＨＲＹＵＡＳＬＪ＜Ａ＇ＬＡＮＧＬＥＹ"]}, {"box": [344, 1077, 544, 1095], "vertical": false, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["ＮＡＧＥＡＫＡＷＯＲＪ"]}], "img_path": "004.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 800, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [700, 62, 763, 165], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["あなたがどこに", "行こうと", "私はいつもあなたを", "見てるわ"]}, {"box": [425, 127, 465, 199], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["自分の進む", "道は"]}, {"box": [384, 200, 435, 267], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["あなたが", "自分で", "決めるのよ"]}, {"box": [192, 66, 270, 86], "vertical": false, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["碇シンジ"]}, {"box": [58, 124, 346, 219], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["本編の主人公。１０年以上も", "の間、伯父の家に預けられ", "て育つ。突然、父・ゲンドウによりネルフに", "呼ばれエウァのパイロットとなる。（１４歳"]}, {"box": [192, 242, 288, 266], "vertical": false, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["葛城ミサト"]}, {"box": [194, 233, 217, 242], "vertical": false, "font_size": 12.0, "lines": ["かつら"]}, {"box": [0, 67, 26, 201], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["登場人物紹介"]}, {"box": [390, 309, 406, 481], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["進むことを決意する．．．。"]}, {"box": [58, 302, 344, 396], "vertical": false, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["ネルフ本部戦術仕事も普段イベントは", "局第一課所属。シンジの直", "最の上司にあたる。おおらかな性格でシン", "ジの数少ない理解者。花の独身．．．。（２５歳）"]}, {"box": [192, 423, 290, 444], "vertical": false, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["碇ゲンドウ"]}, {"box": [58, 481, 343, 578], "vertical": false, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["シンジの実父。特務機関ネ", "ルフの最高司令長官。任務", "至上主義で実の息子にも冷徹だが、レイに", "は不思議な思いやりを見せる。（４８歳）"]}, {"box": [407, 297, 769, 932], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["●前巻までのあらすじ", "全て行政機の開催があるまでエンジンを持ってから、「お", "が実行された。心を固く閉ざしたシシンに拒否され一時は失敗したかに見えたが、", "意識の波の中シンシは母子イと向き合っていた。自分の進むべき道は自分で決め", "るのよ。私はいつでもあなたを見ているわ。と優しく声をかけられ、心を開いた", "シンジはついに生還する。その騒ぎの直後、今度は冬月が拉致される。ゲンドウ", "の行動を問題視しているゼーレが冬月に情報提供を要求する為だった。だが、そ", "れを拒否しづづける今月は一方で過去の事を回想していた。ゲンドウ・ユイとの", "出会い、セカンド・インバクト、アダム育生計画、エヴァ第号機、人類補究計画", "そしてネルフの誕生．．．！様々な過去を回想している時、加持が現れ解放される。", "だがその行動は加持にとっては最後の仕事になってしまう。何者かによって殺さ", "れてしまう加持。加持の秘密の言葉をふけ取ったミサトは泣き崩れながらも前に"]}, {"box": [189, 600, 268, 625], "vertical": false, "font_size": 25.0, "lines": ["綾波レイ"]}, {"box": [61, 659, 343, 756], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["零号機のパイロット。マル", "ドゥック機関の＞報告書によ", "って選ばれたフアースト・チルドレンとし", "ラ以外の経歴は不明の謎のお美少女。（１４歳"]}, {"box": [189, 782, 309, 825], "vertical": false, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["惣流アスカ・", "ラングレー"]}, {"box": [167, 840, 342, 883], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["ドイツから来た弐号機のパ", "イロット。頭脳明脈、操縦"]}, {"box": [741, 925, 756, 958], "vertical": true, "font_size": 14.0, "lines": ["これで"]}, {"box": [707, 956, 719, 1020], "vertical": true, "font_size": 14.0, "lines": ["ジ．．．エンドか"]}, {"box": [57, 890, 338, 935], "vertical": false, "font_size": 18.5, "lines": ["センス抜群の完全無敵のパーフェクト美少", "女（性格以外）。（４歳）"]}, {"box": [190, 962, 263, 983], "vertical": false, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["渚カヲル"]}, {"box": [59, 1019, 345, 1115], "vertical": false, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["フィフス・チルドレン。生", "年月日がセカンド・インパク", "トと同一日という他、それ以外の情報はす", "さて抹消済みといいう謎につつまれた美少年"]}], "img_path": "005.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 800, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [], "img_path": "006.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 800, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [51, 64, 182, 87], "vertical": false, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["ＳＴＡＧＥＡ７"]}, {"box": [360, 521, 414, 539], "vertical": false, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["．．．"]}], "img_path": "007.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 800, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [648, 350, 706, 418], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["ママ", "聞いて"]}, {"box": [66, 525, 115, 623], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["あたし", "選ばれたの"]}, {"box": [618, 719, 720, 894], "vertical": true, "font_size": 29.0, "lines": ["人類を守る", "エリートパイロット", "なのよ"]}, {"box": [73, 953, 174, 1098], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["大勢の中から", "あたしが", "選ばれたの"]}], "img_path": "008.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 800, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [681, 100, 740, 186], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["あたしとくべっち", "特別なの"]}, {"box": [315, 76, 363, 133], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["だから", "ママ"]}, {"box": [397, 242, 475, 350], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["ママの望んだ", "通りになった", "のよ"]}, {"box": [77, 274, 129, 355], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["こっちを", "向いて"]}, {"box": [223, 662, 279, 799], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["あたしが自力で", "倒した使徒は"]}, {"box": [60, 1033, 118, 1114], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["たったの", "１体．．．"]}], "img_path": "009.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 800, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [644, 57, 725, 179], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["それも", "太平洋艦隊の", "力を借りて．．．"]}, {"box": [609, 468, 697, 587], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["その次は", "ファーストと", "３人で"]}, {"box": [22, 294, 138, 452], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["次の使徒は", "シンジと一緒じゃ", "なければ", "倒せなかった"]}, {"box": [682, 745, 711, 863], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["その次と次は"]}, {"box": [230, 556, 309, 676], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["あたしはただ", "命令通り", "動いただけ"]}, {"box": [275, 997, 333, 1098], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["手も足も", "出なかった"]}], "img_path": "010.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 800, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [651, 60, 708, 158], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["倒したのは", "両方とも"]}, {"box": [131, 133, 189, 254], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["無敵の", "シンジ様．．．か"]}, {"box": [694, 540, 724, 635], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["教えてママ"]}, {"box": [368, 363, 426, 500], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["あたしは本当に", "特別なの．．．？"]}, {"box": [232, 602, 282, 699], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["アスカ", "聴こえる？"]}, {"box": [406, 996, 437, 1093], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["加持さん．．．"]}], "img_path": "011.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 800, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [623, 521, 712, 620], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["いつも通り", "余計な事は", "考えないで"]}, {"box": [43, 495, 112, 596], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["やってる", "わ！"]}, {"box": [49, 765, 104, 832], "vertical": true, "font_size": 28.0, "lines": ["いつも", "通りよ"]}, {"box": [654, 912, 708, 1087], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["．．．どうしたんでしょう", "アスカ"]}, {"box": [580, 960, 637, 1078], "vertical": true, "font_size": 32.0, "lines": ["調子が出ないみたいですね"]}, {"box": [577, 958, 628, 1079], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["調子が出ない", "みたいですね"]}, {"box": [49, 907, 103, 1044], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["困ったわね", "この忙しい時に"]}], "img_path": "012.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 800, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [668, 104, 747, 224], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["やはりレイの", "零号機を優先", "させましょう"]}, {"box": [67, 317, 155, 454], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["今は同時に", "修理できる", "ゆとりはないわ"]}, {"box": [681, 567, 708, 645], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["シンジ君"]}, {"box": [99, 662, 186, 781], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["学校は", "いつまで休む", "つもりなの？"]}, {"box": [121, 884, 144, 933], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["え？"]}], "img_path": "013.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 800, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [580, 83, 715, 225], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["体の方はもう", "いいんでしょう？", "もう何ヶ月も", "学校に行って", "ないんでしょ？"]}, {"box": [58, 91, 110, 155], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["え．．", "えーと"]}, {"box": [691, 361, 715, 457], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["行かないと"]}, {"box": [438, 423, 459, 521], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["ダメですか"]}, {"box": [50, 400, 105, 536], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["行きづらいのは", "わかるわ"]}, {"box": [638, 594, 718, 753], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["でもあなたの仕事は", "エヴァ操縦だけじゃ", "ないのよ"]}, {"box": [383, 612, 461, 673], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["勉強も", "仕事の", "ひとつ"]}, {"box": [273, 590, 343, 731], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["でも", "アスカは？", "まだ寝てますけど"]}, {"box": [49, 597, 188, 758], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["アスカは", "大学出てるから", "いいのッ", "人の事はどうでも", "いいでしょッ"]}, {"box": [522, 953, 625, 1095], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["もうひとつ言えば", "あなたを学校へ", "行かせるのも", "私の仕事なのよ"]}], "img_path": "014.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 800, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [715, 78, 736, 138], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["でも．．"]}, {"box": [491, 71, 521, 150], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["辛いのは"]}, {"box": [103, 141, 159, 279], "vertical": true, "font_size": 23.0, "lines": ["あなただけじゃ", "ないのよ"]}, {"box": [613, 431, 641, 512], "vertical": true, "font_size": 21.0, "lines": ["シンジ君"]}, {"box": [441, 330, 517, 454], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["みんな辛いけど", "がんばって仕事", "してんのよ"]}, {"box": [658, 638, 684, 700], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["はい．．"]}], "img_path": "015.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 800, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [271, 70, 314, 176], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["ミサトさんは", "ああ言うけど"]}, {"box": [50, 162, 129, 287], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["学校へなんか", "行けるワケ", "ないじゃないか"]}, {"box": [255, 359, 314, 480], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["僕はトウジを", "殺したんだ．．．"]}, {"box": [641, 626, 691, 724], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["ケンスケや", "委員長に"]}, {"box": [245, 646, 335, 786], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["どんな顔して", "逢えばいいって", "いうんだ"]}], "img_path": "016.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 800, "img_height": 1200, "