ue, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["弐号機を"]}, {"box": [60, 1041, 79, 1093], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["いいえ"]}], "img_path": "152.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 800, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [684, 58, 741, 175], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["お手並み", "拝見といくわ"]}], "img_path": "153.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 800, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [683, 374, 698, 430], "vertical": true, "font_size": 13.0, "lines": ["くて．．．"]}, {"box": [423, 373, 501, 481], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["前はあんなに", "戦うのがイヤ", "だったのに"]}, {"box": [67, 430, 121, 573], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["待つのがこんなに", "つらいなんて"]}, {"box": [610, 595, 714, 719], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["また僕だけ", "こんな所で", "手をこまねいて", "いるだけなのか"]}, {"box": [288, 630, 338, 724], "vertical": true, "font_size": 24.0, "lines": ["これでもし", "また"]}, {"box": [65, 695, 116, 819], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["綾波とかに", "何かがあったら"]}, {"box": [646, 931, 669, 1049], "vertical": true, "font_size": 22.0, "lines": ["．．．あったら"]}, {"box": [89, 983, 124, 1057], "vertical": true, "font_size": 26.0, "lines": ["僕は．．"]}], "img_path": "154.jpg"}, {"version": "0.1.6", "img_width": 800, "img_height": 1200, "blocks": [{"box": [673, 123, 704, 247], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["膠着状態ですね"]}, {"box": [662, 505, 737, 664], "vertical": true, "font_size": 18.0, "lines": ["まず敵の", "攻撃手段が", "読めないことには．．．"]}, {"box": [404, 499, 480, 658], "vertical": true, "font_size": 19.0, "lines": ["青からオレンジへ", "パターンが周期的に", "変化しています"]}, {"box": [675, 833, 748, 956], "vertical": true, "font_size": 20.0, "lines": ["マギは", "回答不能を", "提示しています"]}, {"box": [80, 687, 124, 758], "vertical": true, "font_size": 16.0, "lines": ["どういう", "こと？"]}, {"box": [420, 843, 498, 970], "vertical": true, "font_size": 17.0, "lines": ["答えを導くには", "データ不足と", "いうわけね"]}, {"box": [110, 1001, 137, 1044], "vertical": true, "font_size": 27.0, "lines": ["た